aldercroft

Class Line

  • java.lang.Object
    • aldercroft.Line

  • public class Line
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the Line objects with an ID and the X,Y-Coordinates of the starting and ending point. It also provides the basic functionality to get and set the values of the variables.
    Author:
    Franziska Blumenschein, Tobias Renner
